Subject: drm/amdkfd: add pinned BOs to kfd_bo_list
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 4fac4fcf4500bce515b0f32195e7bb86aa0246c6
